"Phat Loot, No Work" - The Druid Motto</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#313532><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/udyninvifargent.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Dynin Vifargent</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/anim_1.gif BORDER=0 HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Protector of Underfoot</span><br>  Posts: 1166<br> <font color=#CC9900>(2/1/01 12:23:15 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: ***DISCUSSION*** -- Vox/Nag time limit proposal</span><hr size=1> why are we expressing our opinion ?<br>
