<br>
Just speaking my peace, and I know there has to be some determination on what to consider holidays that are globally acceptable.  The idea is that we can actually reduce some of the times, rather then extend them, while giving some (rare - only two cases) a better opportunity to succeed .. go easy on me /plead<br>
